# Quiz Example - General Knowledge

show window "General Knowledge Quiz"

question "What is the capital of France?" choices "London", "Paris", "Berlin", "Madrid"
question "Which planet is known as the Red Planet?" choices "Venus", "Jupiter", "Mars", "Saturn"
question "What is 2 + 2?" choices "3", "4", "5", "6"
question "Who wrote Romeo and Juliet?" choices "Dickens", "Shakespeare", "Austen", "Hemingway"

end quiz

run window